      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything feels so empty lately. i used to feel like there was this constant hum of music in my head, something driving me, you know? but now its just... silence. like the person who used to make things is just gone. i look in the mirror and i dont even see a person anymore, just a hollow shell where the art used to be. it feels pointless to keep going when there is nothing left inside to express.",
