    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help, but it feels like they're trying to help a ghost. they see the body, they see the person walking around, but they dont realize the part that actually mattered is dead. the music, the vision, the soul of everything... it's just gone. it feels like i'm just an empty container carrying around a corpse. how can you even talk about \"getting better\" when the essence of who i am isn't even there anymore?",
